        <p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><b>Users Share Their 
          WeatherBug Stories</b></font></p>
        <p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">In last month's 
          Bug Bytes, we asked you, our WeatherBug Community, to share with us 
          your WeatherBug stories. We received many great responses! Thank you 
          to everyone who participated! Click <a href="http://www.weatherbug.com/BugBytes/Apr2003_part2.htm#Story3" target="BugStories">here</a> 
          to read some of our favorite stories...</font></p>
        <p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">If you did not have 
          a chance to send us your WeatherBug story last month, or if you have 
          a new story to share with us, please feel free to send an email at any 
          time to <a href="mailto:story@weatherbug.com">story@weatherbug.com</a>. 
          Also, please feel free to submit a picture of yourself. We will be checking 
          for new emails often, and will continue to share your stories with other 
          members of the WeatherBug Community.</font></p>
        <p><font size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">To submit a story 
          or picture, you must be over the age of 13. By submitting your story, 
          you are granting WeatherBug permission to use your quote and picture 
          on WeatherBug.</font></p>
